<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَإِذَا الْجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتْ <span class="c2">(١٢)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
