<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عَلِمَتْ نَفْسٌ ما أَحْضَرَتْ <span class="c2">(١٤)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١٠٨- وَإِذَا الْبِحارُ فُجِّرَتْ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَإِذَا الْقُبُورُ بُعْثِرَتْ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>عَلِمَتْ نَفْسٌ ما قَدَّمَتْ وَأَخَّرَتْ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>يا أَيُّهَا الْإِنْسانُ ما غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ الْكَرِيمِ <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>الَّذِي خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّاكَ فَعَدَلَكَ <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فِي أَيِّ صُورَةٍ ما شاءَ رَكَّبَكَ <span class="c2">(٨)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>كَلَّا بَلْ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِالدِّينِ <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَإِنَّ عَلَيْكُمْ لَحافِظِينَ <span class="c2">(١٠)</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>كِراماً كاتِبِينَ <span class="c2">(١١)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>يَعْلَمُونَ ما تَفْعَلُونَ <span class="c2">(١٢)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>إِنَّ الْأَبْرارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٍ <span class="c2">(١٣)</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَإِنَّ الْفُجَّارَ لَفِي جَحِيمٍ <span class="c2">(١٤)</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>يَصْلَوْنَها يَوْمَ الدِّينِ <span class="c2">(١٥)</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>وَما هُمْ عَنْها بِغائِبِينَ <span class="c2">(١٦)</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>وَما أَدْراكَ ما يَوْمُ الدِّينِ <span class="c2">(١٧)</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>ثُمَّ ما أَدْراكَ ما يَوْمُ الدِّينِ <span class="c2">(١٨)</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>يَوْمَ لا تَمْلِكُ نَفْسٌ لِنَفْسٍ شَيْئاً وَالْأَمْرُ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِلَّهِ <span class="c2">(١٩)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>١٠٩- فَلْيَنْظُرِ الْإِنْسانُ مِمَّ خُلِقَ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>خُلِقَ مِنْ ماءٍ دافِقٍ <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>يَخْرُجُ مِنْ بَيْنِ الصُّلْبِ وَالتَّرائِبِ <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>إِنَّهُ عَلى رَجْعِهِ لَقادِرٌ <span class="c2">(٨)</span><a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>يَوْمَ تُبْلَى السَّرائِرُ <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>فَما لَهُ مِنْ قُوَّةٍ وَلا ناصِرٍ <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
