<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>مَا الْقارِعَةُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>وَما أَدْراكَ مَا الْقارِعَةُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>يَوْمَ يَكُونُ النَّاسُ كَالْفَراشِ الْمَبْثُوثِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
